  "title": "chore(examples): add app style for word wrap in e-commerce demo",
  "body": "<!--\r\n  Thanks for submitting a pull request!\r\n  Please provide enough information so that others can review your pull request.\r\n-->\r\n\r\n**Summary**\r\n\r\nThis adds style to `app.css` to wrap words.\r\nIt fixes the glitches (1) and (2) from [here](https://github.com/algolia/angular-instantsearch/pull/629#issuecomment-506790740).\r\n\r\n**Result**\r\n\r\n- [Without it](https://develop--instantsearchjs.netlify.com/examples/e-commerce/?refinementList%5Bbrand%5D%5B0%5D=HP&refinementList%5Bbrand%5D%5B1%5D=Speck&refinementList%5Bbrand%5D%5B2%5D=Epson): ← open it on small browser.\r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/499898/60442813-2546f200-9c1a-11e9-9c2e-47afbb10b67d.png)\r\n\r\n- [With it](https://deploy-preview-3913--instantsearchjs.netlify.com/examples/e-commerce/?refinementList%5Bbrand%5D%5B0%5D=HP&refinementList%5Bbrand%5D%5B1%5D=Speck&refinementList%5Bbrand%5D%5B2%5D=Epson): ← open it on small browser.\r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/499898/60442861-3f80d000-9c1a-11e9-89b4-f013e34af01f.png)\r\n",
